%page

A Bigger Universe: all 95 printable ASCII Characters


	Arabic numbers? just ten possible digits

	UPPER or lower-case letters: 26 characters

	UPPER and lower-case, plus number: 62 characters

	Another 33: : ; < = > ? @ { | } ~ [ ] ^ _ ` ! " # $ % & ' ( ) * + , - . / \ and a space


